ZH: 我们要在二点钟出发。
EN: We need to leave at 2 o'clock.

ZH: 我家有二个孩子。
EN: I have two children in my family.

ZH: 这个星期是二月份。
EN: This week is in February.

ZH: 红绿灯倒数到二就可以过马路了。
EN: The traffic light turns green when it counts down to two.

ZH: 我见过他二次。
EN: I have seen him twice.

ZH: 昨晚我睡了二十个小时。
EN: I slept for twenty hours last night.

ZH: 如果情况紧急，请拨打二。
EN: If it's an emergency, please dial two.

ZH: 二加二等于四。
EN: Two plus two equals four.

ZH: 我给你二个苹果。
EN: I'll give you two apples.

ZH: 这里有二百美元。
EN: There are two hundred dollars here.

ZH: 我家门牌号是二十二号。
EN: The number of my house is twenty-two.

ZH: 昨天我在超市买了二瓶水。
EN: I bought two bottles of water at the supermarket yesterday.

ZH: 请帮我找到第二个章节。
EN: Please help me find the second chapter.

ZH: 我已经错过了前两辆公交车。
EN: I have already missed the first two buses.

ZH: 我的生日是二月二十号。
EN: My birthday is on the 20th of February.

ZH: 请每位同学回答二个问题。
EN: Please answer two questions each, students.

ZH: 他两个月大的时候开始说话。
EN: He started speaking when he was two months old.

ZH: 这是我第二次来中国。
EN: This is my second time visiting China.

ZH: 他是我二哥，我还有一个弟弟。
EN: He is my second older brother, I also have a younger brother.

ZH: 请从第二页开始阅读。
EN: Please start reading from the second page.
